Troubleshooting¶

  • If you are on can’t see SimNIBS commands in your Linux or OSX terminal, be sure that you are using a bash terminal, not tcsh

  • If you are experiencing problems during the install, be sure that you can connect to https://repo.continuum.io/ and https://github.com/

  • Please send an email to support@simnibs.org including the simnibs_install_log.txt file, which can be found in your SimNIBS installation directory
